quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  67,27,"Falamma raawhu zulfatan see-atwujoohu allatheena kafaroo waqeela hatha allatheekuntum bihi taddaAAoon"
  67,28,"Qul araaytum in ahlakaniya Allahuwaman maAAiya aw rahimana faman yujeeru alkafireenamin AAathabin aleem"
  67,29,"Qul huwa arrahmanu amannabihi waAAalayhi tawakkalna fasataAAlamoona man huwa fee dalalinmubeen"
  67,30,"Qul araaytum in asbaha maokumghawran faman ya/teekum bima-in maAAeen"
  68,1,"Noon walqalami wama yasturoon"
  68,2,"Ma anta biniAAmati rabbika bimajnoon"
  68,3,"Wa-inna laka laajran ghayra mamnoon"
  68,4,"Wa-innaka laAAala khuluqin AAatheem"
  68,5,"Fasatubsiru wayubsiroon"
  68,6,"Bi-ayyikumu almaftoon"
  68,7,"Inna rabbaka huwa aAAlamu biman dallaAAan sabeelihi wahuwa aAAlamu bilmuhtadeen"
  68,8,"Fala tutiAAi almukaththibeen"
  68,9,"Waddoo law tudhinu fayudhinoon"
  68,10,"Wala tutiAA kulla hallafinmaheen"
  68,11,"Hammazin mashsha-in binameem"
  68,12,"MannaAAin lilkhayri muAAtadin atheem"
  68,13,"AAutullin baAAda thalika zaneem"
  68,14,"An kana tha malinwabaneen"
  68,15,"Itha tutla AAalayhi ayatunaqala asateeru al-awwaleen"
